1 2. An analysis estimating any potential increase or decrease in the
2 amount of residential construction in the Commonwealth.
3 (b) The analyses required under paragraph (a) of this subsection shall be:
4 1. Completed prior to and included with the submission of the
5 administrative regulation to the committee under subsection (8) of this
6 section; and
7 2. Included as an attachment to the administrative regulation when it is
8 filed with the Legislative Research Commission in accordance with
9 KRS Chapter 13A.
